# Obsolete as of 2013 & no longer used or maintained

UC Davis Faculty Recruitment Application, located at https://recruitments.ucdavis.edu/.

Recruitments is widely used across the UC Davis campus.  The following are some basic usage statistics (generated March 2011):

* 30 campus units across 7 schools utilize Recruitments
* 54 positions recruited, 18 currently accepting apps
* 2,428 applications have been created, 1,820 of those submitted
* 15,809 files have been uploaded by applicants (that's a lot!)
* 936 distinct committee members have reviewed applications

A CAES Dean's Office production.
